properties.name: Alamere Falls via Coast Trail from Palomarin Trailhead
Parking and Trailhead
properties.desc: Park at the Palomarin parking lot and start walking northwest on the trail that leads along the coast.

properties.name: Coastal View
properties.desc: A great viewpoint of the Pacific Ocean. On a clear day you can see the Farallon Islands!

properties.name: Bass Lake
properties.desc: Small lake on the way. Some people enjoy swimming in this lake as a break from the hike.  If you want to take a dip, follow the trail leading down to the lake.

properties.name: Bottom of Alamere Falls
properties.desc: This is the bottom of the tierd falls, be careful during high tide
